	<h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>
	<p class="about-paragraph">We are a  team of technologists and storytellers. We are working on an amazing platform that will convert all your favorite movies,shows and videos into easy and fun to read comic books.</p>
  <p class="about-paragraph">Over decades, innumerable number of movies, from various cultures, have entertained us. Over generations, many television shows have touched our lives. Educational videos have made our learning that much more interesting and real. Our revolutionary technology and processes will reformat all of the above and more into  exciting comic e-books that you can read anytime, anywhere.</p>
  <p class="about-paragraph">We are a globally distributed team with a wide range of expertise amongst ourselves, ranging from decades of experience in cutting-edge technology development to the media and entertainment industry.</p>
  <p class="about-paragraph">Above all we have the passion to create something new and exciting that everyone can enjoy!</p>
